data.description: Beautiful well maintained home located on a quiet street in Chester. This home boasts a level fenced in back yard with an in-ground chlorine pool (new liner in 2021).  The shed in the back and the unfinished 1/2 story provide extra storage space if needed.  The detached garage is a great space for whatever your needs are, to place your car or having a workshop for your tools and hobbies.
